{"tid":1200802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去得野餐就一定要食下罐頭","createTime":"2019-06-10T23:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T00:18:46.000Z","uid":182006,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67b1570b69f9a8621ab7b924c304388a88cbdb2d","tid":1200802,"uid":182006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GKVzNVG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGKVzNVG.png&h=3bbbfe7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前幾年開始，很多火紅的youtuber<br />\n都在自家後院打開一罐神秘罐頭<br />\n一開就捏鼻，直嚷著很臭<br />\n到底有多臭呢?<br />\n聞不到就讓我用數據告訴你！<br />\n<br />\n關鍵中的臭味細菌「Haloanaerobium」，在發酵過程中除了會製造出二氧化碳，來降低其他細菌孳生，得以延長魚肉保存外，還會帶有異味的化學物質如乙酸、丙酸、丁酸及硫化氫等。<br />\n<br />\n「乙酸」有著醋的酸酸味道。<br />\n「丙酸」帶有刺鼻的感覺。<br />\n「丁酸」會有腐臭油脂味。<br />\n「硫化氫」聞起來就像臭雞蛋氣味。<br />\n<br />\n日本NHK曾以Alabaster儀器測量世界多款獨具臭味的食物後，結果鹽醃鯡魚以8070 Au臭味值揮低其他臭物。(Alabaster Unit是一種儀器，Au是測量臭味的單位)<br />\n <br />\n前十一名排行榜如下：<br />\n1. 瑞典 鹽醃鯡魚 (Surstr&ouml;mming)：8070 Au<br />\n2. 韓國 洪魚膾 (Hongeohoe)：6230 Au<br />\n※ 發酵鰩魚<br />\n3. 紐西蘭 罐裝乳酪 (Epicure Cheese)：1870 Au<br />\n4. 愛斯基摩 醃海雀 (Kiviak)：1370 Au<br />\n※ 將生海雀塞進生海豹裡發酵的肉類食品<br />\n5. 烤的日本臭魚乾 (焼きたてのくさや)：1267 Au<br />\n6. 日本 鮒壽司 (ふなずし): 486 Au<br />\n※ 發酵鮒魚<br />\n7. 日本 納豆 (なっとう): 452 Au<br />\n8. 烤前的日本臭魚乾 (焼く前のくさや): 447 Au<br />\n9. 日本 黃蘿蔔乾 (沢庵漬け): 430 Au<br />\n10. 臭豆腐: 420 Au<br />\n11. 越南魚露: 390 Au<br />\n*  臭襪子: 120 Au<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lifechem.tw/blog/170802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lifechem.tw%2Fblog%2F170802&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=82b0815f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lifechem.tw/blog/170802</a>"},{"pid":"2a6988b3f4f56f1d40fd58ac9986bb8cb66a1c79","tid":1200802,"uid":182006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:42:12.000Z","msg":"知唔知邊度有得買 好想請啲議員食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bc6342edf553e7a455f9689f5f45bfaf0c02cb","tid":1200802,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:48:13.000Z","msg":"有興趣自己買罐嚟食<br />\n唔知邊度有得賣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2732b458abecc42d2e55ee1c9984660f37c7a07","tid":1200802,"uid":1265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:55:33.000Z","msg":"好似好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4947335ba2e27e92ed4a2e1b94c285f0589b9208","tid":1200802,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T23:57:06.000Z","msg":"一罐點夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超碼2-3罐開心share"},{"pid":"dd59c5adfc97c84e53a50d5aa67a371107d553ce","tid":1200802,"uid":182006,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H93BgZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH93BgZa.png&h=ffba82d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有無人鐘意玩顏料氣球？"},{"pid":"2ad1b5b99efe8586b652d5b1cd6450b2ff50b458","tid":1200802,"uid":182006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:12:09.000Z","msg":"其實液體既然是要灌水， <br />\n<br />\n只要使用的顏料沒有特別限制， <br />\n<br />\n個人認為水彩顏料是很好的選擇， <br />\n<br />\n一盒水彩，便宜，顏色也多樣 <br />\n<br />\n且以分裝成小條， <br />\n<br />\n易於裝填入氣球 <br />\n<br />\n先將顏料擠入氣球中 <br />\n<br />\n再拿到水龍頭下灌水 <br />\n<br />\n水沖入時即已混和完成， <br />\n<br />\n不夠就再搓柔搓柔囉！ <br />\n<br />\n放久會沉澱，在搓搓即可<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/tw.answers.yahoo.com/amp/qna/20070608000010KK09150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Ftw.answers.yahoo.com%2Famp%2Fqna%2F20070608000010KK09150&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=fe2dbee7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/tw.answers.yahoo.com/amp/qna/20070608000010KK09150</a>"},{"pid":"dd4d559972cb75c073328a83d0ab736baae501e1","tid":1200802,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:12:20.000Z","msg":"乙酸 丙酸 丁酸 硫化氫 四樣都可以做武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9098ca033842c36963f48be4c09066b9e0b686ee","tid":1200802,"uid":50882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:13:00.000Z","msg":"同屎比邊個臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905600a971a466076fa69709b270cf52f9987bfd","tid":1200802,"uid":150133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:15:23.000Z","msg":"納豆開水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a90588a534b116a7c0afc744188f23a0dd9bc9c","tid":1200802,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:15:46.000Z","msg":"開一罐入去<br />\n嚇到佢地封鎖立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7a3611bd957ecd50cdfeec553c0e051d976a15","tid":1200802,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:16:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce3d2bc54463a9ae9ad6cb2d12a0d52f38195aa1","tid":1200802,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a90588a534b116a7c0afc744188f23a0dd9bc9c","tid":1200802,"uid":248275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:15:46.000Z","msg":"開一罐入去<br />\n嚇到佢地封鎖立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:18:46.000Z","msg":"不明氣體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}